  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个项目创建一个甘特图，时间范围是2014年1月。整体标题就叫\"A Gantt Diagram\"吧。日期格式用YYYY-MM-DD，这样比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，标题设为\"A Gantt Diagram\"，日期格式用YYYY-MM-DD。那任务怎么划分呢？需要分几个阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分两个主要部分吧。第一个section叫\"Section\"，里面有两个任务：第一个任务\"A task\"从2014年1月1日开始，持续30天，给它一个标识a1；第二个任务\"Another task\"要等第一个任务完成后才开始，持续20天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Section",
        "A task",
        "a1",
        "2014-01-01",
        "30d",
        "Another task",
        "after a1",
        "20d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第一个section已经加上，\"A task\"从1月1日开始30天，标记为a1，\"Another task\"依赖a1，完成后开始，20天。第二个section怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Section",
        "A task",
        "Another task"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个section叫\"Another\"。里面第一个任务\"Task in Another\"从1月12日开始，做12天。还有一个\"another task\"，这个要等前面的任务完成后自动开始，持续24天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Another",
        "Task in Another",
        "2014-01-12",
        "12d",
        "another task",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下第二个section：\"Task in Another\"从2014-01-12开始12天，\"another task\"在它之后开始，持续24天。这样两个section的任务都设置好了，您看对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Another",
        "Task in Another",
        "another task"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对的，注意\"another task\"是小写的，和前面的\"Another task\"区分开。另外检查一下，第一个section里的依赖关系是\"after a1\"，第二个section里的\"another task\"没有显式写after，但默认就是接在\"Task in Another\"后面吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "another task",
        "after a1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Mermaid里如果省略after，默认就是按顺序依赖前一个任务。所以\"another task\"会自动接在\"Task in Another\"之后。所有设置都确认无误了，我这就生成最终的甘特图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "another task",
        "Task in Another"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
